{{Infobox TV channel | name = ATN ZoOm | logofile = Zoom TV.jpg | logocaption = '''Zoom TV logo''' | logosize = | launch = February 17, 2011 | closed date = | picture format = | network = | owner = [[Asian Television Network]] | slogan = | country = [[Canada]] | broadcast area = National | headquarters = [[Newmarket, Ontario]] | former names = | web = [http://www.asiantelevision.com/ZOOM.htm ATN ZoOm] | sat serv 1 = | sat chan 1 = | cable serv 1 = [[Rogers Cable]] | cable chan 1 = Channel 696 | iptv serv 1 = [[Bell Fibe TV]] | iptv chan 1 = Channel 791 }} '''ATN Zoom''' (stylized ''zoOm'') is a [[Television in Canada|Canadian]] [[Category B Services|Category B]] [[Hindi language]] [[specialty channel]] that is owned by [[Asian Television Network]] (ATN). It broadcasts programming from [[Zoom (TV channel)|ZoOm]] as well as [[Canadian content]].
ATN Zoom is an [[India]]n entertainment channel whose sole focus is [[Bollywood]] and the Indian entertainment industry. It features entertainment news, interviews with the top stars, movie reviews, music and more.
